post:
Hi guys!

&lt;br /&gt;

As promised, some good deals are here. HostHatch was founded on 11th April, 2011 and today marks the 8th year in existence. These are special deals that will be available for one week.

&lt;br /&gt;

We won't be extending these and the orders will close on 18th April.

&lt;br /&gt;

We're also introducing Chicago in these deals. The looking glass is available at http://lg.chi.psychz.net/ - very premium network. Provisioning ETA for Chicago servers is 29th April, 2019. (Expected ~20th April, but the promised date is 29th April) -- all the equipment is already there. 
&lt;br /&gt;

Chicago storage:
&lt;pre&gt;
Base plan:
1x 3.0 GHz
3 GB RAM
3 TB usable storage
15 TB bandwidth
$84 per year
Add more: 1 GB RAM, 1 TB storage and 5 TB bandwidth chunks for $2.5 per month each. Up to 30 TB storage per VM. This pricing is only for servers created until 18th April.
&lt;/pre&gt;


&lt;pre&gt;
Note: We can do this plan on monthly billing if at least 5 TB storage is bought.
Note2: Servers can be upgraded with chunks after the promotion period at the same pricing, as long as the server was ordered within the promotional period.
Note3: Sorry for making it a bit confusing, could not figure out a way to make the structure easier.
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;

NVMes:

&lt;pre&gt;
1 CPU core (15% dedicated)
512 MB RAM
8 GB NVMe disk (RAID-10)
1 TB premium bandwidth
$15 per year
Available in: Oslo, Vienna, NY, LA, Chicago, Stockholm and Amsterdam
Free upgrade with double RAM in any location
Free upgrade with double RAM, double disk, and 10x bandwidth in Chicago
Free 40 Gbps DDoS protection will be activated for Chicago NVMe customers at a later date (will be available at a cost for orders after 18th April)
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;
1 CPU core (30% dedicated)
1 GB RAM
10 GB NVMe disk (RAID-10)
1 TB premium bandwidth
$30 per year
Available in: Oslo, Vienna, NY, LA, Chicago, Stockholm and Amsterdam
Free upgrade with double RAM in any location
Free upgrade with double RAM, double disk, and 10x bandwidth in Chicago
Free 40 Gbps DDoS protection will be activated for Chicago NVMe customers at a later date (will be available at a cost for orders after 18th April)
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;
Any of our larger NVMe plans (if paid semi-annual or higher):

Free upgrade with double RAM in any location
Free upgrade with double RAM, double storage, and 10x bandwidth in Chicago + free DDoS protection
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;

Storage plans (available in Amsterdam, Stockholm, Chicago - not LA)

&lt;pre&gt;
1 CPU core
512 MB RAM
250 GB storage
1 TB bandwidth
$15 per year
(small amount available in each location, thread will be updated once sold out) 
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;
1 CPU core
1 GB RAM
1 TB storage
4 TB bandwidth
$12 per quarter
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;br /&gt;

We cannot replace existing servers, or apply these promotions to existing servers. These only apply to new servers ordered before 18th April.

&lt;br /&gt;

**To order:**

To order, please sign up/login at manage.hosthatch.com and deposit the appropriate amount of funds. Then open a ticket with sales mentioning the promotion/location you want. All servers will be created by us manually with the following provisioning times and renewal dates will be updated accordingly:


Chicago: 29th April
Amsterdam/Stockholm: 19th April
NY/LA/Oslo/Vienna: 24 hours

&lt;br /&gt;

All of these are approximate, we will try to deliver much earlier where possible. We do not expect any delays in provisioning times more than these dates. Please read this thread carefully before depositing funds.

&lt;br /&gt;

Thank you for the love guys. To the next 8 years and more. Cheers!
